friday: Here's what's happening, Boss. We've got a social media storm brewing with Gen Z icon Raghav Chadha losing over a million followers overnight due to a massive online backlash. On the geopolitical front, tensions between Israel and Iran are escalating, with Trump cancelling US envoys' visits to Pakistan and the 60-day limit on his 'unauthorised' war on Iran looming. Meanwhile, in India, political drama is unfolding with BJP and AAP leaders trading barbs, and a bus strike in Telangana has finally come to an end, bringing relief to passengers.